    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "\"mental awakening\" is a crazy way to put it, but it actually feels like that. it's not just feeling \"smart,\" it's like my actual biology has changed. i remember being out in the desert last month during that solar storm event and i've been feeling this way ever since. do you think something atmospheric or like, cosmic radiation, could actually trigger a change in how our DNA functions or how our neurons fire?",
